text: Aarsha Chandini Baiju (born 8 November 2000) is an Indian actress who works in Malayalam movies. She made her acting debut in Pathinettam Padi (2019) and later starred in the Karikku Fliq mini-series Average Ambili (2021). She played the female lead in Mukundan Unni Associates (2022).
